This is currently not applicable as 2handed weapon is massively reduced and opening strikes overall now pretty much suck. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uwoodydarogue.showPublicProfile?language=EN>WoodyDaRogue</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/12/02 7:08:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RE</span><hr size=1> 2h weapons suck in my opinion.<br>
<br>
